data.title: JOYALUKKAS Trademark of Joy Alukkas Jewellery LLC
data.meta_description: JOYALUKKAS is a trademark of Joy Alukkas Jewellery LLC. Filed in April 8 (2009), the JOYALUKKAS covers Jewelry; precious and semi-precious stones; diamonds; watches and parts and fittings therefor; precious metals; clocks coated with precious metal and their parts and fittings
